# Session [2] – Network+

## Main Topics
- Hub chist? (what is hub?)
- Hub chetor kar mikonad? (how does hub work?)
- Fargh hub ba switch chist? (what is the difference between hub and switch?)

## Flashback – Hub Basics
- Hub = device ke chand PC ra be ham vasl mikonad
- Hub **data ra be tamame port ha broadcast mikonad** (na faghat PC mored nazar)
- Hub device simple (bi jan hast) , na smart 

## Explanation
- Hub = hardware baraye network
- Hame PC ha ra be ham vasl mikonad
- Data ra be tamame PC ha miresand (ine kamel nist, chon bandwidth ra divide mikonad)
- Fargh switch:
  - Switch device smart tar ast, data ra faghat be port mored nazar miresand
- Estefade dar LAN haye koochik ya test network

